{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/GIF_Slammers_Short_HD.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><br>--BEFORE YOU BUY!-- </strong><i>(Please read this if you want to buy this game) </i><strong>--</strong>The game is still expected to receive big changes. Even though it is out of EA, content will continue to be added <strong><i>for now</i></strong>.\u00a0 <br>THE CHANGES PLANNED:<br>- Game to be turned into a dungeon crawler<br>- Due to the above point, local coop will be discontinued (its also hard on a solo dev).<br>- No more heroes, you will have your own character with adjustable stats like in a normal ARPG<br>- Classless<br> <i><strong>THESE CHANGES ARE NOT GUARANTEED TO OCCUR.</strong></i>\u00a0I will keep you updated on the progress of these items on the pinned steam discussion post.<br><strong>--<br>----------------------- </strong><i><br>Hack! Slash! Dodge! Spin! Slam!\u00a0Cast!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Realtime Action with MOBA design sprinkled with bullet-hell dust? You're covered here sir.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/GifMagus.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">CODE:BLUE is an attempt to combine fun elements from many genres into one package. Wanted to whirlwind but also knock enemies up? You're covered. Auto-Battler With Hack&amp;Slash? Why not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/WarrenSpearGIF1.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wanted to spam AA with attack speed items but also be able to dodge with i-frames? Why would you want that... anyways that's in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/GifFrank2.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources in the round, buy skills and talents in the intermission, then kick some ass.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But wait, do you have enough damage or did you spend all your resources on movement speed? I don't know, maybe? You should probably think about your build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/Gif_WarrenComboSequenc.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Top-down action <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/GIF_WinstonBubbleTradeHD.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 4 Abilities Per Hero + Additional Shop Ability </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Combine various upgrades together to achieve your desired build</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Defeating Enemies grants money which you can then spend on upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Upgrades stack, boosting their effect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Receive Elemental Crystals and assign them to your abilities or your body</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Dodge Bullets and Attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/GIF_CaptainNew2.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 8 Heroes with their own unique abilities  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 4.5 Elemental Types </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 200+ Upgrades, each with a distinct effect  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 4 Main levels, with a choice to loop infinitely </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Constantly increasing difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 50+ Steam Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167100/extras/GifFrank.gif?t=1737037299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A discord is present if you wish to join it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controller: You can play this game with a controller (<strong>you need controllers for local co-op</strong>) but UI navigation with a controller is not available. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Music by Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio and Android128, Icons from </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rookie Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/817ba1083121ae42343227c6be1ea51767fd3666.jpg"},{"name":"Junior Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/f89bffed789655bb66f49603aae9732abf89bfdf.jpg"},{"name":"Apprentice Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/872dfb58e527c1e1d80a3ac338abb917c533367e.jpg"},{"name":"Peerless Rookie Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/c8f320e732cad2b5753125488a112b0f2885f472.jpg"},{"name":"Peerless Junior Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/6e9e47a48449e52437350dba03b2ef9ec335d35d.jpg"},{"name":"Peerless Apprentice Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/0c9a9dba0900cc3573af4c0137c921db212cd6ff.jpg"},{"name":"Inimitable Rookie Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3167100/6068910208d1e53cb1166eac08b14b27a2282e0e.jpg"},{"name":"Inimitable Junior Horde Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps